-- Saudi Intelligence Warns of Possible Terror Attack in Europe, France Says
-- B y   G r e g o r y   V i s c u s i
-- 2010-10-17T17:48:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-17/saudi-intelligence-warns-of-possible-terror-attack-in-europe-france-says.html
Saudi Arabia’s intelligence services
warned several days ago of a possible terror attack “on the
European continent, notably in France” by an al-Qaeda offshoot,
French Interior Minister Brice Hortefeux said on an LCI
television talk show today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
